snippet.title: Concursion Gameplay Trailer #3
snippet.description:
Imagine a world of bright blue skies and puffy white clouds. You sprint across platforms, jump over gaps, and bounce off of an enemy... only to find yourself in outer space...

Concursion is a fusion of five classic gaming genres, molded into one seamless experience.

Available now for PC and Mac.
http://www.ConcursionGame.com
http://www.facebook.com/PuubaInc
